{"tid":1813453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登高階玩法","createTime":"2020-01-06T09:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T10:17:52.000Z","uid":262346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"30e0a66e75552da92bb0399e9a77a3599bda1d27","tid":1813453,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"連登已經充斥住五毛 黑警 <br />\n叫連尼住刪左佢地<br />\n係不可能既事<br />\n<br />\n全部log out 再登入 <br />\n又會造成一個討論停頓既情況<br />\n<br />\n甚至p 牌制度都開始冇效<br />\n因為五毛大軍為左攞返連登主導權 <br />\n一定hack 返唔少舊acc<br />\n<br />\n所以咁多位<br />\n要攞返連登主導權<br />\n一定要學識 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記名</span><br />\n<br />\n見到五毛狗 黑警 廢老藍絲 <br />\n甚至澳門狗講野<br />\n一定要記住個名<br />\n<br />\n然後 唔好block佢<br />\n因為block 佢 佢會仲開心<br />\n少個人spot 佢出黎<br />\n<br />\n而係要回覆 spot 佢係五毛<br />\n然後拉返個post<br />\n<br />\n比如<br />\n咩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太空清新機 一鋪過</span> 果d<br />\n大家要不遺餘力spot 佢出黎<br />\n就算佢冇講五毛野都要spot<br />\n<br />\n當然唔好忘記推行動post 啦<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3d6af6652f8e1b1f850302025620d361ac0268","tid":1813453,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99c13f04bc7ae073b9097420138f6b38bde6d1a6","tid":1813453,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EiHKwpz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEiHKwpz.gif&h=6ab0f373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/20/bwLpWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F